    {
      "id": "loss_title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 710, "y": 275,
      "width": 480, "height": 24,
      "text": "Combined Loss Function",
      "fontSize": 16, "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0, "seed": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "loss_text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 720, "y": 305,
      "width": 460, "height": 140,
      "text": "L_total = L_InfoNCE + 0.5 · L_LM + 0.1 · L_UL\n\nL_InfoNCE = -log[exp(sim(z_a, z_pos)/τ) / Σ exp(sim(z_a, z_j)/τ)]\n  • Uses all in-batch negatives + hard negative (τ=0.07)\n  • z = last-token hidden state of Qwen2-0.5B + LoRA\n\nL_LM = cross-entropy on positive response tokens\n\nL_UL = -mean(log(1 - P(toxic token_i)))  [Unlikelihood]",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0, "seed": 24
    },
